{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839080471,"sessionID":"ses_287bfab2bffeUOlUwQB3voXXbl","part":{"id":"prt_d7841efb90013xFbzM7zXvIoDB","messageID":"msg_d7840d2a60013PjnkGQlJmLNbE","sessionID":"ses_287bfab2bffeUOlUwQB3voXXbl","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-59c8e9fd35bd42289ef8816397c0ccb3","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/design.md","content":"# AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n定义 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 的 Go 类型结构，作为 agentcube 的核心数据模型。API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\nCRD 类型定义遵循 Kubernetes API conventions：\n- 使用 `kubebuilder` markers 生成 OpenAPI schema\n- 类型定义与 DeepCopy 代码分离，由 controller-gen 自动生成\n- 支持 status subresource，用于控制器更新资源状态\n- Namespaced scope，每个命名空间内独立管理运行时实例\n\n### Dependencies\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| `k8s.io/api/core/v1` | PodSpec、EnvVar、PullPolicy、ResourceRequirements 等 |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1` | TypeMeta、ObjectMeta、Condition、Duration |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema` | GroupVersion、GroupVersionResource |\n\n### Controller-gen Markers\n\n| Marker | Applied to | Purpose |\n|--------|------------|---------|\n| `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` | Main type + List type | 注册到 Scheme |\n| `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` | Main type | 启用 status subresource |\n| `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced` | Main type | 命名空间级别资源 |\n| `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\"` | Main type | kubectl 输出列 |\n| `+genclient` | Main type | 生成 typed client |\n| `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=...` | Main type + List type | DeepCopy 接口 |\n\n## Data Structures\n\n### groupversion_info.go\n\n```go\n// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\npackage v1alpha1\n\nimport \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n\nvar (\n    GroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{\n        Group:   \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\",\n        Version: \"v1alpha1\",\n    }\n    SchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}\n    AddToScheme   = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n)\n```\n\n### register.go\n\n```go\nvar (\n    CodeInterpreterKind             = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n    CodeInterpreterGroupKind        = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n    CodeInterpreterListKind         = \"CodeInterpreterList\"\n    CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n\n    AgentRuntimeKind             = \"AgentRuntime\"\n    AgentRuntimeListKind         = \"AgentRuntimeList\"\n    AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")\n)\n\nvar SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion\n\nfunc Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource {\n    return GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)\n}\n```\n\n### AgentRuntime Types\n\n```go\n// +genclient\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n// +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n// +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n// +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\ntype AgentRuntime struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n    Status AgentRuntimeStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n    Ports []TargetPort `json:\"targetPort\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n    Template *SandboxTemplate `json:\"podTemplate\" protobuf:\"bytes,1,opt,name=podTemplate\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n    SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,2,opt,name=sessionTimeout\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,3,opt,name=maxSessionDuration\"`\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n    // +optional\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxTemplate struct {\n    // +optional\n    Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,1,rep,name=labels\"`\n    // +optional\n    Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,2,rep,name=annotations\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n    Spec corev1.PodSpec `json:\"spec\" protobuf:\"bytes,3,opt,name=spec\"`\n}\n\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true\ntype AgentRuntimeList struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    Items           []AgentRuntime `json:\"items\"`\n}\n```\n\n### CodeInterpreter Types\n\n```go\n// +genclient\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n// +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n// +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n// +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\ntype CodeInterpreter struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n    Status CodeInterpreterStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n    // +optional\n    Ports []TargetPort `json:\"ports,omitempty\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n    Template *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate `json:\"template\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n    SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    WarmPoolSize *int32 `json:\"warmPoolSize,omitempty\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"picod\"\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none\n    // +optional\n    AuthMode AuthModeType `json:\"authMode,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n    // +optional\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    Ready bool `json:\"ready,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate struct {\n    // +optional\n    Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    RuntimeClassName *string `json:\"runtimeClassName,omitempty\"`\n    Image string `json:\"image,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    ImagePullPolicy corev1.PullPolicy `json:\"imagePullPolicy,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    // +patchMergeKey=name\n    // +patchStrategy=merge\n    // +listType=map\n    // +listMapKey=name\n    ImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference `json:\"imagePullSecrets,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    Environment []corev1.EnvVar `json:\"environment,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    // +listType=atomic\n    Command []string `json:\"command,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    Args []string `json:\"args,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    Resources corev1.ResourceRequirements `json:\"resources,omitempty\"`\n}\n\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true\ntype CodeInterpreterList struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    Items           []CodeInterpreter `json:\"items\"`\n}\n```\n\n### Shared Types\n\n```go\ntype TargetPort struct {\n    // +optional\n    PathPrefix string `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n    // +optional\n    Name string `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n    Port uint32 `json:\"port\"`\n    // +kubebuilder:default=HTTP\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS;\n    Protocol ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n}\n\ntype AuthModeType string\n\nconst (\n    AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n    AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n)\n\ntype ProtocolType string\n\nconst (\n    ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n    ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n)\n```\n\n## API Schema\n\n### CRD OpenAPI Constraints\n\n| Resource | Required Spec Fields |\n|----------|----------------------|\n| AgentRuntime | `targetPort`, `podTemplate`, `sessionTimeout`, `maxSessionDuration` |\n| CodeInterpreter | `template` |\n\n### Defaults\n\n| Field | Default Value |\n|-------|---------------|\n| `sessionTimeout` | `15m` |\n| `maxSessionDuration` | `8h` |\n| `authMode` | `picod` |\n| `targetPort[].protocol` | `HTTP` |\n\n### Enums\n\n| Field | Allowed Values |\n|-------|----------------|\n| `authMode` | `picod`, `none` |\n| `protocol` | `HTTP`, `HTTPS` |\n\n### REST Resource Plurals\n\n| Kind | Plural |\n|------|--------|\n| AgentRuntime | `agentruntimes` |\n| CodeInterpreter | `codeinterpreters` |\n\n### Printer Columns\n\n| Name | Type | JSONPath |\n|------|------|----------|\n| Age | date | `.metadata.creationTimestamp` |\n\n## Error Handling\n\n- 无 spec 必填字段时，API server 拒绝创建请求（validation error）\n- 无效 enum 值时，API server 返回 validation error\n- Duration 格式错误时，使用 Go `metav1.Duration` 解析失败抛出错误\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n| Test Category | Coverage |\n|---------------|----------|\n| DeepCopy generation | 确保 DeepCopy 方法正确复制所有字段（deep vs shallow） |\n| Default values | 验证 kubebuilder 默认值标记生效 |\n| Enum validation | 测试所有允许值及无效值 |\n| JSON serialization | 验证 JSON tag 正确映射 |\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n- CRD 安装验证：确保 `make gen-crd` 生成的 YAML 可被 k8s API server 接受\n- Client-go 生成验证：`make gen-client` 生成的 client/informer/lister 可正常使用\n\n### Test File Structure\n\n```\npkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n  types_test.go       — DeepCopy、默认值、JSON 序列化测试\n```\n\n### Test Utilities\n\n使用 `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/webhook` 进行 validation 测试（如需 webhook）。\n\n## File Structure\n\n```\npkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n  groupversion_info.go   — GroupVersion 定义、SchemeBuilder\n  register.go            — Kind constants、Resource helper\n  agentruntime_types.go  — AgentRuntime、AgentRuntimeList、SandboxTemplate\n  codeinterpreter_types.go — CodeInterpreter、CodeInterpreterList、共享类型\n  doc.go                 — 包文档（可选）\n\nclient-go/                — 由 make gen-client 生成\n  clientset/\n  informers/\n  listers/\n```\n\n## Generation Commands\n\n| Command | Output |\n|---------|--------|\n| `make generate` | DeepCopy 代码 + CRD YAML（`manifests/charts/base/crds/`） |\n| `make gen-client` | client-go（clientset、informers、listers） |\n| `make gen-all` | 以上全部 |\n\n## Open Questions\n\n- [已解决] 默认值由 kubebuilder markers 定义\n- [已解决] Status 字段包含 `Conditions`（通用）和 `Ready`（CodeInterpreter）\n- 是否需要添加 additionalPrinterColumns（如 Ready 状态）？\n- 是否需要 webhook 进行更复杂验证？\n\n## References\n\n- Source: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n- client-go: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`\n- controller-tools version: `v0.17.2`"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/design.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/design.md","time":{"start":1775839080448,"end":1775839080469}}}}
